article_metadata.description: The Ohio Department of Medicaid held a hearing recently on the proposed Healthy Ohio plan which would fundamentally alter the aid that so many of my fellow citizens need (Dispatch article, Tuesday). It is just another conservative attempt to undermine the progress made through the Affordable Care Act and nickel-and-dime those who need help the most.
